item.title: 'List of CSI: Crime Scene Investigation episodes
item.description: The following is a list of episodes from the CBS television series, “CSI: Crime Scene Investigation” in which Jorja Fox appeared or was credited. Episodes are rated based on quality and volume of Jorja’s scenes. Episodes in which she is listed in the credits but does not appear are rated with zero stars. Season One # Title Airdate Rating 1 "Pilot" Oct 6, 2000 Grissom investigates a suicide that presents little evidence.
